13.install axios (npm install axios)

14 install strip library for card functionality(npm i @stripe/stripe-js)and (npm i @stripe/react-stripe-js)
15.sign up stripe.com  coppy api key.and go to app.js and write "const promise=loadstripe("your api key here")"
